    <id>https://community.sap.com/t5/sap-codejam-blog-posts/sap-codejam-hana-ml-in-wroc%C5%82aw-2024-10-recap/ba-p/13929019</id>
    <title>SAP CodeJam HANA ML in Wrocław 2024-10 Recap</title>
    <updated>2024-11-05T13:55:58.300000+01:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Vitaliy-R</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/183</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;At the end of October, we had the Getting Started with Machine Learning using SAP HANA and&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;A class="" href="https://community.sap.com/t5/c-khhcw49343/Python/pd-p/f220d74d-56e2-487e-8e6c-a8cb3def2378" target="_blank"&gt;Python&lt;/A&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;SPAN&gt;in Wrocław, Poland, kindly hosted by LeverX and organized by&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/1728320"&gt;@Olena_Nadtochii&lt;/a&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-center" image-alt="ImportedPhoto.751973070_w.jpg" style="width: 999px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/187002iA6FF77C0CCA1D927/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="ImportedPhoto.751973070_w.jpg" alt="ImportedPhoto.751973070_w.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P class=""&gt;We had a fantastic group of participants, ranging from seasoned SAP veterans...&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-center" image-alt="ImportedPhoto.751973070_wide.jpg" style="width: 999px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/187003i2DE0A44564C71835/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="ImportedPhoto.751973070_wide.jpg" alt="ImportedPhoto.751973070_wide.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;...to fresh talents who recently graduated from university.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-center" image-alt="ImportedPhoto.751973037_wide.jpg" style="width: 999px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/187004i326F80975E0C3D5D/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="ImportedPhoto.751973037_wide.jpg" alt="ImportedPhoto.751973037_wide.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;This SAP CodeJam took place in a historical building—the former seat of the Faculty of Pharmacy of Wrocław University: a part of the university buildings'&amp;nbsp;frontage, stretching along the Odra River in the northern part of the Old Town. The view from the top was breathtaking: from the&amp;nbsp;&lt;A href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wroc%C5%82aw_Cathedral" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Gothic&lt;/SPAN&gt; Cathedral&lt;/A&gt; on the right to Concordia Design on the left&lt;SPAN&gt;—&lt;/SPAN&gt;the &lt;A href="https://boty.archdaily.com/us/2021/candidates/135851/concordia-design-wroclaw-slash-mvrdv" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;Building of the Year 2021&lt;/A&gt;, according to ArchDaily.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-center" image-alt="IMG_6049_w.jpg" style="width: 999px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/187005iE712174D8EC6060A/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="IMG_6049_w.jpg" alt="IMG_6049_w.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;And the food was equally fabulous.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-center" image-alt="IMG_6052_wide.jpg" style="width: 999px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/187009iDD53FBACD33F7E6E/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="IMG_6052_wide.jpg" alt="IMG_6052_wide.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P class=""&gt;I’d like to thank all the participants who joined me for this final SAP CodeJam of 2024!&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-center" image-alt="ImportedPhoto.751981248_wide.jpg" style="width: 999px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/187011iAF43DAA8BA28677E/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="ImportedPhoto.751981248_wide.jpg" alt="ImportedPhoto.751981248_wide.jpg" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P class=""&gt;The 2024 tour included 14 stops for me, and now it has come to an end.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Now, the next stops are in 2025, and I hope to see you in Spain (&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/107"&gt;@ajmaradiaga&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;), UAE (&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/45547"&gt;@athavanraja&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;), India (&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/141830"&gt;@Shilpa_Shankar&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;).&amp;nbsp;&lt;SPAN&gt;Would you like to host such an SAP CodeJam in your location? Here are the details:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;A href="https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-blogs-by-sap/quot-getting-started-with-machine-learning-using-sap-hana-quot-as-a-new-sap/ba-p/13574098" target="_blank"&gt;https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-blogs-by-sap/quot-getting-started-with-machine-learning-usin...&lt;/A&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/sap-codejam-blog-posts/sap-codejam-hana-ml-in-wroc%C5%82aw-2024-10-recap/ba-p/13929019"/>
    <published>2024-11-05T13:55:58.300000+01:00</published>
  </entry>
